'''''475: Break the Silence,''''', (Umutwe wumwimerere: ''475: Trenquem el Silenci'' ) ni Sinema yo muri Maroc yo muri 2013 yerekana filime ngufi iyobowe na Hind Bensari <ref>https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/475-break-the-silence</ref>.   Iyi filime yibanze ku buzima bwa Amina Fillali, umukobwa w’imyaka 16 ukomoka mu mujyi muto muri [[Maroc]]<ref>https://burnsfilmcenter.org/booking/475-break-the-silence/</ref>. Yiyahuye afata uburozi bwimbeba amaze gushyingiranwa numugabo wamusambanyije.<ref>https://www.bartleby.com/essay/Zainab-Salbis-475-Break-The-Silence-PCKFC4TBTWB</ref>   Yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya filime ryita ku burenganzira bwa muntu mu 2014<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film860680.html</ref>. 

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://www.duhoctrungquoc.vn/wiki/ha/475:_Break_the_Silence</ref>.  Yagize uruhare mu myigaragambyo muri [[Maroc]] gushyiraho itegeko rishya ryemerera abagabo baregwa gufata ku ngufu gushyingiranwa n’abo bahohotewe<ref>https://theweereview.com/review/475-break-the-silence/</ref>. Iyi filime yamamaye cyane mu kinyamakuru New York Times no mu muyoboro wa ARD wo mu [[Budage]] ndetse no kuri interineti.<ref>https://www.mostrafilmsdones.cat/475-break-the-silence/</ref>  yemeje kandi abayireba kuri TV 2M muri [[Maroc]] kandi isakaza mu bindi bihugu birimo [[Danimarike|Danemark]], [[Porutugali]], [[Kanada]] kandi igurishwa ku miyoboro irenga 20 ku isi.<ref>https://www.festivalmarrakech.info/en/personnalite/hind-bensari/</ref>

